 "Bihar, India (Muzaffarpur region). Local traditional variety.", "traits": "Local variety characteristics.", "flesh_fruit": "Good quality suitable for local markets.", "yield_notes": "Reliable production in Bihar conditions.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "", "sort_order": 9}, {"name": "Gulabi", "slug": "gulabi", "lineage_type": "indigenous", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "Bihar and West Bengal, India. Traditional variety.", "traits": "Pinkish hue to skin, distinctive coloration. Fragrant aroma.", "flesh_fruit": "Sweet with pleasant fragrance. Good quality.", "yield_notes": "Good production.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "Available from Bihar and West Bengal nurseries.", "sort_order": 10}, {"name": "Swarna Roopa", "slug": "swarna-roopa", "lineage_type": "indigenous", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "Developed by Central Horticultural Experiment Station (CHES), Ranchi, Jharkhand, India. Modern Indian breeding selection.", "traits": "Selected for specific improved characteristics including crack resistance.", "flesh_fruit": "High TSS (Total Soluble Solids) content. Small seeds. Excellent quality.", "yield_notes": "Good productivity.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "Available from CHES Ranchi and Jharkhand nurseries.", "sort_order": 11}, {"name": "Green", "slug": "green", "lineage_type": "indigenous", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "India, traditional variety.", "traits": "Distinctive green characteristics maintained longer.", "flesh_fruit": "Good quality when fully mature.", "yield_notes": "Reliable production.", "growing_notes": "", "availability": "Available from Kerala nurseries.", "sort_order": 12}, {"name": "Early Large Red", "slug": "early-large-red", "lineage_type": "indigenous", "climate_slug": "tropical-monsoon", "origin": "India, developed variety.", "traits": "Large fruit size with bright red coloration. Early maturity.", "flesh_fruit": "Good quality, sweet flavor.", "yield_notes": "Good 